  "text": "# ONLINE & MOBILE BANKING  \n**Q: Is online banking secure?**\nA: Yes. We use bank-level security (TLS 1.3 encryption, two-factor authentication, 15-minute session timeout).  \n**Q: Do you have a mobile app?**\nA: Yes. Download \"FirstUK Bank\" from Apple App Store or Google Play Store (iOS 13+, Android 9+).  \n**Q: Can I use biometric login?**\nA: Yes. Mobile app supports fingerprint and face ID for quick, secure access.  \n**Q: Can I transfer money from home banking?**\nA: Yes. Online banking and mobile app both support money transfers to other banks (1–2 business days).  \n**Q: Is my data private?**\nA: Completely. We comply with GDPR and never share your data with third parties for marketing.  \n---",
